text: Eduardo Arrillaga (born 28 September 1961) is a Mexican rower. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Mexico Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
